  "detailed_description": "Fight as an unknown warrior with various weapons, and dive into The Forest of Souls to find the souls of Lost Ancient Kings.<br>Challenge them and get their power, then finally face your terminative destiny.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Third-person lite action game</h2>This is a indie game that focus on boss fight.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Slay to unlock more weapons</h2>As you kill more enemies, you can unlock new weapons which have unique attack style.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948330/extras/dd3fbe1b18cb6b67a9ffb064caa25c9d.avif?t=1650092688\" width=600 height=264 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Learn battle skills from different weapons</h2>Every weapon has different battle style, light attack combo, heavy attack etc. Learn to make use of your weapon through fights.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948330/extras/224140c943a69bef863b114b0682bff1.avif?t=1650092688\" width=720 height=404 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Find ancients to challenge the souls of Lost Ancient Kings</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948330/extras/1aa7ee3c092ba724eae7bbb8d86311c5.avif?t=1650092688\" width=720 height=404 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948330/extras/b59db1b238dfba634eb07d5a370b168e.avif?t=1650092688\" width=650 height=352 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hardcore difficulty</h2>Enemies are highly aggressive and powerful, death is common.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948330/extras/deb84e2f6e73e87ef79f22a31845a2ee.avif?t=1650092688\" width=720 height=404 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Spend souls to gain power</h2>Though you might die many times, you can spend souls you collect to upgrade your weapon to challenge again.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948330/extras/b0e83eb7bea09ed736d4578ef94d2c96.avif?t=1650092688\" width=650 height=366 /></span>",
